{
  "stem": "10710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went to the border also on black-- it was a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They told us to go in the wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Like unfortunately, we were with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was in Ital-- and we went from Austria at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "From Austria there were the British.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the British didn't want you to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They didn't want to let anybody into Israel because they occupied Israel at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was the mandate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then didn't let the Jews go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So at night, we had to go into-- when they didn't see, we were going to the wagons, laid down straight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they used to come with the flashlights but didn't see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They never looked on the bottom, so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But what happened one night we went, and they forgot to attach our wagon to the other train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So the train went away and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But so we went the next night we went through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "When we came to Italy it was like we come to paradise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Beautiful country and the people were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Really nice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Then I went to-- I was in camp Cremona.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I came in 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "DP camp, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were about, I would say, about 1,500 people in that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody was there was going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this was the illegal boats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what happened, they used to catch the boats, and they put the people to Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Behind wires again in another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, no, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My friends, we decided we are not coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would wait until we could go legal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided not to go to Israel because we didn't want to be in the camp again.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
